    "synopsis": "After the companion or Yenna, survives the battle with Orin. They would leave the party as a temporary follower and take some time to recover from their ordeal before returning to camp.In Yenna's case, she will reappear after hiding somewhere safe during the combat.Players can talk to them briefly before they return to camp where the companion/Yenna will also disappear from the temple back to camp.",
    "how_to_trigger": "1) Start game as DU2) Go to Bhaal Temple3) Talk to Orin by getting spotted.4) Make sure abductee isn't killed in dialog with skillchecks.5) Defeat Orin.6) PostBattleDarkUrge should trigger.7) Resist Bhaal when he offers DU to be chosen one.8) DU dies, Withers appears and resurrects everyone.9) Abductee would also be awakened from the altar (if they survived the battle).10) Talk to Abductee."
  },
